snippet.title: Barbie - C64 full playthrough
snippet.description:
The telephone rings, and Barbie rush to answer the phone. It is Ken (the boyfriend).
Ken Want´s to take Barbie out on a date. Barbie jumps in her red sports car. And drive down the main street, looking for the right outfit. If Barbie don´t find the right combination of clothing. There will be no date.

Barbie Playlist:
